          For all markers, amplification of <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">20</NUMEX> ng genomic <ENAMEX TYPE="SUBSTANCE">DNA</ENAMEX> in a
          total reaction mix of <NUMEX TYPE="QUANTITY">10 Î</NUMEX>¼l was performed according to
